analysis.description:
Crowdsale.checkCrowdsaleState (/unique_chucks/3/0x0c411fffc6d3a8e4ca5f81bbc98b5b3eda8fc3c7.sol#237-268) uses a dangerous strict equality:
	- tokensIssued == maxCap && crowdsaleState != state.crowdsaleEnded

Reentrancy in Crowdsale.claimTeamTokens (/unique_chucks/3/0x0c411fffc6d3a8e4ca5f81bbc98b5b3eda8fc3c7.sol#408-457):
	External calls:
	- assert(bool)(tokenTotalSupply > ERC20TokenInterface(tokenAddress).totalSupply()) (/unique_chucks/3/0x0c411fffc6d3a8e4ca5f81bbc98b5b3eda8fc3c7.sol#442-447)
	- mintAmount = tokenTotalSupply - ERC20TokenInterface(tokenAddress).totalSupply() (/unique_chucks/3/0x0c411fffc6d3a8e4ca5f81bbc98b5b3eda8fc3c7.sol#447-449)
	State variables written after the call(s):
	- foundersTokensClaimed (/unique_chucks/3/0x0c411fffc6d3a8e4ca5f81bbc98b5b3eda8fc3c7.sol#449-450)

Reentrancy in Crowdsale.fallback (/unique_chucks/3/0x0c411fffc6d3a8e4ca5f81bbc98b5b3eda8fc3c7.sol#220-235):
	External calls:
	- require(bool)(KycContractInterface(kycAddress).isAddressVerified(msg.sender)) (/unique_chucks/3/0x0c411fffc6d3a8e4ca5f81bbc98b5b3eda8fc3c7.sol#225)
	State variables written after the call(s):
	- crowdsaleState (/unique_chucks/3/0x0c411fffc6d3a8e4ca5f81bbc98b5b3eda8fc3c7.sol#225-227)

Reentrancy in Crowdsale.processTransaction (/unique_chucks/3/0x0c411fffc6d3a8e4ca5f81bbc98b5b3eda8fc3c7.sol#301-336):
	External calls:
	- InsurePalTokenInterface(tokenAddress).mint(_contributor,tokensToGive) (/unique_chucks/3/0x0c411fffc6d3a8e4ca5f81bbc98b5b3eda8fc3c7.sol#322-326)
	State variables written after the call(s):
	- contributorList (/unique_chucks/3/0x0c411fffc6d3a8e4ca5f81bbc98b5b3eda8fc3c7.sol#326-328)
	- tokensIssued (/unique_chucks/3/0x0c411fffc6d3a8e4ca5f81bbc98b5b3eda8fc3c7.sol#330-333)
mintAmount in Crowdsale.claimTeamTokens (/unique_chucks/3/0x0c411fffc6d3a8e4ca5f81bbc98b5b3eda8fc3c7.sol#413) is a local variable never initialiazed

KycContract.salvageTokensFromContract (/unique_chucks/3/0x0c411fffc6d3a8e4ca5f81bbc98b5b3eda8fc3c7.sol#147-161) does not use the value returned by external calls:
	-ERC20TokenInterface(_tokenAddress).transfer(_to,_amount) (/unique_chucks/3/0x0c411fffc6d3a8e4ca5f81bbc98b5b3eda8fc3c7.sol#152-161)

Crowdsale.salvageTokensFromContract (/unique_chucks/3/0x0c411fffc6d3a8e4ca5f81bbc98b5b3eda8fc3c7.sol#345-354) does not use the value returned by external calls:
	-ERC20TokenInterface(_tokenAddress).transfer(_to,_amount) (/unique_chucks/3/0x0c411fffc6d3a8e4ca5f81bbc98b5b3eda8fc3c7.sol#351-353)

Reentrancy in Crowdsale.fallback (/unique_chucks/3/0x0c411fffc6d3a8e4ca5f81bbc98b5b3eda8fc3c7.sol#220-235):
	External calls:
	- require(bool)(KycContractInterface(kycAddress).isAddressVerified(msg.sender)) (/unique_chucks/3/0x0c411fffc6d3a8e4ca5f81bbc98b5b3eda8fc3c7.sol#225)
	- processTransaction(msg.sender,msg.value) (/unique_chucks/3/0x0c411fffc6d3a8e4ca5f81bbc98b5b3eda8fc3c7.sol#232-234)
